# Deep Learning

Deep Learning has received a lot of hype in recent years due to its impressive performance on many applications, including language translation, medical diagnosis from X-rays, recognizing images to help with self-driving cars, beating the top Go players as well as beating high-ranking DotA players, learning how to play Atari games just from the pixel data… all these to name a few of Deep Learning’s recent accomplishments! In this post, we will (gently) introduce you to the inner workings behind Deep Learning at an intuitive level.
